source.name: School Breakfast Participation and Meals Served Data
source.description: The School Breakfast Program (SBP) provides cash assistance to States to operate nonprofit breakfast programs in schools and residential childcare institutions.   Data here consists of participation, breakfast meals served, and cash provided to states, all by year, month and current. (format: html, xls)
